product.title: Kawaii Corgi Dog Bone Print Women's Tee
product.body_html:
Are you a dog lover? 

Why not express your love for corgis by wearing this tee when you go out or even at home as a pyjama. Featuring a cute illustrated corgi waving and a dog bone flying by.

This tee is suitable for all genders and ages above the age of 6.

Details

  • Made from 50% Polyester & 50% Cotton
  • Crew neck design
  • Short sleeve


Choose between 6 different sizes and 12 different tee colors. We always recommend going 1-2 sizes up.

Heat Transfer Printing Technology

Heat transfer printing uses the process of heat to transfer an image created in wax to an object or garment. This printing method is compatible with pre-painted images on a wax sheet or can be used to create an image by layering wax dye onto an object.

All printing methods have different advantages that they bring to the table. Heat transfer printing is widely used as it creates durable, heat resistant, adhesive and water-resistant designs. Additionally, the colors created in the image are high resolution with bright and bold colors.

Care & washing pointers

  • Wash less
  • Wash with similar colors
  • Wash cold/warm
  • Wash (and dry) inside out
  • Use the right (amount of) detergents
  • Do not tumble dry
  • Iron on reverse
  • Store correctly
  • Treat stains immediately!
